name: [LORA] Victorian Mix Style
description:
I made the Victorian Mix model's style into LORA. It's good for you to enjoy it together.
The effect is further increased when Detail Tweaker LoRA (细节调整LoRA) is used together. It is a good LORA, so please use it.

当细节调整LoRA合用时，效果会进一步增强。 那是好的LORA，希望一定要使用。
